Slugslinger pressed the button, the airlock opening, followed by the
sucking void of space. He leapt into the air, letting the suction pull
him into outerspace, then backwards, until he transformed into his jet
mode, and his thrusters slowly corrected him. Caliburst looked around at
space, from the inside. He had seen it so many times, it was just
"different" somehow. Probably something about him knowing that he might
die soon.
